                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-116-off646 t18321129-116-cd647"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18321129-116-victim1093" type="victimName">
